posting_body: Discover gracious living at The Trails of Woodlake, a warm and welcoming apartment community located in exciting Houston.
Trails of Woodlake offers a wonderful way of life.
With 17 Serene Wooden Acres by a lovely Natural Bayou.
This amazing community includes Two Swimming Pools and Scenic Views!
Contact our friendly and caring office team today and come see for yourself why Trails of Woodlake is the ideal place for you and your family.
Trails of Woodlake is an apartment located in Harris County and the 77063 ZIP Code.
This area is served by the Houston Independent attendance zone.
